              >part of the images by svstudioart</a
            >
            on Freepik - Some illustrations by
            <a
              class="text-muted text-decoration-none"
              href="https://icons8.com/illustrations/author/zD2oqC8lLBBA"
              >Icons 8</a
            >
            from
            <a
              class="text-muted text-decoration-none"
              href="https://icons8.com/illustrations"
              >Ouch!</a
            >
          </span>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div>

